1) Method Reference for Static Method
<<class-name>>::methodName

2) Method Reference for the Instance Method of a Particular Object
<<object-name>>::methodName

3) Method Reference for the Instance Method of an Arbitrary Object
<<object-type>>::methodName
eg :- Integer::compareTo

4) Method Reference for Constructor
<<class-name>>::new
 // create the list of student objects from names
 Student[] students =  studentNames.stream().map(Student::new).toArray(Student[]::new);

